{
  "notes": [
    "Aging reactions for VBS NOx dependent SOA scheme from Shrivastava et al. (2019)",
    "Using a trick to reuse the VBS NOX DEPENDENT reactions types :",
    "setting high_nox_yield = 1 and low_nox_yield = 0 for  the fragmentation product",
    "and high_nox_yield =0 and low_nox_yield = 1 for the functionalisation product",
    "the VBS nox dependent reaction behaves like the fragmentation reactions except",
    "that alpha_frag is not limited to 0.75 like in the paper."
